dct_title_s: Scotland energy map 2019 : electricity generation & transmission (including renewable energy sites > 1.0MW) / compiled, designed and produced by La Tene Maps.
dct_description_sm: 1 main map with territorial waters and 3 inset maps of Aberdeenshire Area, Glasgow-Edinburgh and Shetland. Shows renewable and nonrenewable energy generation and transmission sites and power lines. Proposed and actual sites are also shown. Includes legend. "May 2019."
